pageContext.claim: “[O'Rourke] got an F from the NRA, one of the few. You know -- you know what an F means? An F means he wants to take away your guns, OK? That's what it means. I never even heard of an F. I never heard.”
pageContext.analysis: O'Rourke does have an "F" rating from the NRA, but he has said repeatedly that he supports the "preserving the Second Amendment."
